00:22:42,300 --> 00:22:52,780
[Lotus Pavilion]

396
00:22:47,420 --> 00:22:52,300
♫With mild wind and bright sunlight, the flowers look beautiful♫

397
00:22:52,320 --> 00:22:53,000
Mother.

398
00:22:59,720 --> 00:23:01,480
This lady is...?

399
00:23:05,000 --> 00:23:06,760
This is Shi Yi.

400
00:23:07,440 --> 00:23:08,300
Hello, Auntie.

401
00:23:12,680 --> 00:23:14,600
Hello, Miss Shi.

402
00:23:15,200 --> 00:23:16,720
Have you had lunch yet?

403
00:23:17,120 --> 00:23:18,080
I haven't.

404
00:23:20,640 --> 00:23:22,440
It's the Qingming Festival these days

405
00:23:22,440 --> 00:23:23,880
