501
00:29:18,000 --> 00:29:18,840
I don't feel like eating that anymore.

502
00:29:18,840 --> 00:29:20,700
So we came out for something nice.

503
00:29:20,880 --> 00:29:23,280
Miss Shi Yi, would you mind us joining?

504
00:29:24,080 --> 00:29:24,680
Not at all.

505
00:29:24,800 --> 00:29:26,660
This is my cousin, Zhousheng Ren.

506
00:29:28,320 --> 00:29:28,980
They are...

507
00:29:29,040 --> 00:29:29,960
You don't know them.

508
00:29:29,960 --> 00:29:31,160
I'll do the introduction.

509
00:29:31,160 --> 00:29:31,680
Miss Shi.

510
00:29:31,680 --> 00:29:32,680
This is your future brother's wife.

511
00:29:32,680 --> 00:29:33,480
Tang Xiaofu.

512
00:29:33,760 --> 00:29:35,080
That's your future cousin.

513
00:29:35,080 --> 00:29:35,880
Zhou Wenfang.

514
00:29:36,000 --> 00:29:36,640
Hello.

515
00:29:36,960 --> 00:29:37,360
Hello.

516
00:29:38,840 --> 00:29:39,720
Why don't we

517
00:29:39,960 --> 00:29:41,280
