518
00:29:44,800 --> 00:29:45,760
Miss Shi Yi.

519
00:29:46,200 --> 00:29:48,200
Can you stay for several more days this time?

520
00:29:48,200 --> 00:29:49,280
If you're here,

521
00:29:49,360 --> 00:29:50,360
we can have a reason to come out

522
00:29:50,360 --> 00:29:51,490
for something nice.

523
00:29:52,840 --> 00:29:54,280
I'm not staying for long this time.

524
00:29:54,280 --> 00:29:55,210
Maybe next time.

525
00:29:56,440 --> 00:29:58,700
I've been scared to sleep these two days.

526
00:29:59,520 --> 00:30:00,400
Miss Shi Yi.

527
00:30:00,760 --> 00:30:02,000
Would you be afraid

528
00:30:02,160 --> 00:30:03,420
to stay at an old house?

529
00:30:04,280 --> 00:30:05,410
I think I'll be fine.

530
00:30:05,960 --> 00:30:07,040
If I were you,

531
00:30:07,200 --> 00:30:08,280
I'd get out of that place

532
00:30:08,280 --> 00:30:09,280
